Metadata.dc:title: Canoo WebTest White Paper
Metadata.description: Testing is an important part of any serious development effort. For web applications it is crucial. Defects in your corporate website may be only annoying at one time but they can cost you real money at other times, they can lower your market value and may even put you out of business. CWT helps you to reduce the defect rate of your web application.
